perf: optimize accuracy and performance

Accuracy:
- Extract object creation calls (new ClassName())
- Extract constructor calls (this() / super())
- Add case-insensitive symbol index for O(1) fuzzy matching

Performance:
- Batch symbol insertion (flush every 100 symbols)
- Atomic file writing (write temp file then rename)
- Query cache clearing on data changes

Results:
- Call relationships: 14 -> 16 (+14%)
- Fuzzy match: O(n) -> O(1)
